1. Upload all files and folders inside solusvmcontroller folder to you server.
2. Rename configuration.php.default to configuration.php (Please skip this step if your are upgrade from existing installation)
3. Change the file permission of configuration.php to writable. (chmod:777)
4. Access SolusVMController from your browser. E.g. http://yourdomain.com/solusvmcontroller/